&lt;h2&gt;Job Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Compliance Officer to join our Legal &amp;amp; Compliance team. In this role, you will help support and maintain Vise’s compliance program, ensuring we meet our regulatory obligations while enabling our business to grow. You’ll report directly to the Chief Legal Officer (“CLO”) and collaborate closely with teams across the company, as well as the third-party compliance consultant that currently supports the CLO.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a great opportunity for someone with a few years of investment adviser compliance experience in financial services or fintech who wants to take on meaningful responsibility in a fast-paced, mission-driven environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is onsite in NYC, in our SoHo office.&lt;/p&gt;
